---
import CountdownCard from "./CountdownCard.astro";
import CountdownMap from "./CountdownMap.astro";
---

<section class="w-full py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 px-0 relative">
  <div class="container mx-auto relative z-10 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 sm:gap-8 md:gap-10 lg:gap-12">
      <!-- Scroll Above -->
      <img src="/images/elements/scroll-above.svg" alt="" class="w-24 sm:w-32 md:w-40 lg:w-52" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="0" />

       <div class="text-center max-w-full" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="100">
         <h2 class="gradient-text-title text-stroke-gold font-junigarden-swash text-xl xs:text-2xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 leading-tight drop-shadow-lg overflow-x-auto mt-4">
           Langkah kecil hari ini, cerita besar menanti!
         </h2>
         <p class="text-xs xs:text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base lg:text-lg text-white drop-shadow leading-relaxed">
          Ribuan mahasiswa tahun ajaran, bersiaplah menyambut pengalaman luar biasa di Soedirman Student Summit 2026
        </p>
      </div>

      <div data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="200">
        <CountdownCard />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="300" class="w-full">
      <CountdownMap />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mt-12 sm:mt-16 md:mt-20">
      <!-- Scroll Down -->
       <img src="/images/elements/scroll-down.svg" alt="" class="w-24 sm:w-32 md:w-40 lg:w-52 mt-4" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="400" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
